Metadata: AN OVERVIEW OF COMMERCIAL FISHING VESSEL SAFETY IN THE NORTHWEST AND ALTERNATIVES FOR LOSS PREVENTION
University of Washington Sea Grant and University of Alaska Sea Grant

The following information on fishing vessel safety is included in this report: 1. Historical Perspectives. 2. An Approach - Parties in Interest. 3. Recommendations and Conclusions, Specific Problems Identified, Mapping of Interests. Appendix A. A Report of the Second Annual Meeting of the Alaskan Fisheries Safety Advisory Council (AFSAC).
